<LG TYPE="stanza">
<HEAD><I>Sciant presentes &amp; futuri</I> &amp;c<MILESTONE N="97b" UNIT="folio"></HEAD>
<L>wetys ye now all &thorn;at<NOTE PLACE="foot">Ms. <I>yt</I>.</NOTE> bene here</L>
