<DIV2 TYPE="ms"><PB REF="00000143.tif" N="19">
<HEAD>HARL. 2346</HEAD>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>Ihesu kyng of heuene &amp; helle<MILESTONE N="51" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L>Man &amp; womman y wol &yogh;ow telle</L>
