<L>With treson and wi&thorn;-oute gulte</L>
<L>Pore &thorn;u were dryuen a-way</L>
<L>As a best &thorn;at go&thorn; astray</L>
<L>ffro my riche I cam a-doune</L>
<L N="10">To seche &thorn;e fro toune to toune</L>
