<L N="30">Wy&thorn; pride couetise and glotenye<MILESTONE N="51b" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L>Wel he wyst I was a man</L>
<L N="32">But synne in me fond he non
<PB REF="00000147.tif" N="23"></L>
