<L N="105">of<NOTE PLACE="foot">After <I>of</I> in this line there stands in the MS. what looks like a cancelled <I>h.</I></NOTE> bred And wyne the sacramente</L>
<L>for euyr to be youre testament<NOTE PLACE="foot">In the MS. this line was omitted from its place and was written after line 108.</NOTE></L>
<L>the wyche is myne fesche &amp; myne bloode</L>
<L>To tho &thorn;at here levyne vith mylde mode<MILESTONE N="44b" UNIT="folio"></L>
