<L N="15">Wordus of a charter &thorn;at he hath wrow&yogh;th</L>
<L N="16">That &yogh;e mow kepe yn all &yogh;our &thorn;ow&yogh;th
<PB REF="00000173.tif" N="49"></L>
<L N="17">And when &yogh;e &thorn;is boke kan vn&thorn;erstonde</L>
<L>Teche hit forth &thorn;orow all &thorn;is londe</L>
<L>Vntyll o&thorn;er &thorn;at &thorn;is boke haue not sowen</L>
<L N="20">To saue &thorn;eyr sowles ry&yogh;th as &yogh;our owen</L>
