<L>Hys pees he &yogh;eue vs euerychone</L>
<L N="25">Ihesu lord of heuen &amp; helle</L>
<L>Man &amp; wommon y woll &yogh;ow telle</L>
<L>Loke what loue y haue to &thorn;ee</L>
<L N="28">And loke what loue &thorn;ou hast to me</L>
<L N="29">Fro paradys &thorn;ou were out pylte</L>
<L N="30">With kare &amp; sorow &thorn;ou be&thorn; all spylte</L>
<L>And for&thorn;e &thorn;ou bere drawe a-way</L>
